data.description: ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 4.125% INTEREST: Own the best lot in the neighborhood complete with irrigation sprinkler, sleek fence, and a lake view! Enjoy the wildlife on the lake while sipping coffee on the patio. The large lot offers an extensive play area for the kids while the parents grill and enjoy the firepit. The open floor plan of this newer construction 5/3/2 offers a large center island kitchen with SS appliances, granite countertops, and a walk-in pantry. The main level also boasts a flex room, bedroom, bath and under the stairs storage. Upstairs you will find the spacious primary bedroom with his and her walk-in closets. There are 3 more bedrooms, another full bath, and another living area which could be enclosed for a 6th bedroom, but currently is a playroom and movie room. kids. If that's not enough the community offers plenty of playmates and a community pool.  Square footage is received from Volusia County property appraiser records. All information recorded in the MLS is intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
